statements: SELECT * FROM solar_panel_data
SELECT id, panel_id, efficiency FROM solar_panel_data WHERE performance > 0.8
SELECT panel_id, efficiency, performance, timestamp FROM solar_panel_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT id, panel_id, efficiency FROM solar_panel_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY efficiency DESC
SELECT MAX(efficiency), MIN(performance) FROM solar_panel_data
SELECT * FROM solar_panel_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT panel_id, efficiency FROM solar_panel_data WHERE performance > 0.8
SELECT id, panel_id, efficiency, performance, timestamp FROM solar_panel_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-06-30 23:59:59'
SELECT AVG(efficiency) AS avg_efficiency, MAX(performance) AS max_performance FROM solar_panel_data
SELECT * FROM solar_panel_data WHERE efficiency > 0.75 ORDER BY panel_id ASC
SELECT * FROM SolarPanels ORDER BY installation_date DESC
SELECT efficiency, installation_date FROM SolarPanels WHERE efficiency > 0.8
SELECT solar_panel_id, efficiency FROM SolarPanels WHERE efficiency < 0.5 ORDER BY solar_panel_id ASC
SELECT * FROM PanelPerformance WHERE performance_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31'
SELECT SUM(output_power) AS total_power_output FROM PanelPerformance
SELECT * FROM SolarPanels WHERE efficiency > 0.75 ORDER BY installation_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT solar_panel_id, installation_date FROM SolarPanels WHERE efficiency < 0.6 ORDER BY installation_date ASC;

SELECT SolarPanels.*, PanelPerformance.output_power FROM SolarPanels INNER JOIN PanelPerformance ON SolarPanels.solar_panel_id = PanelPerformance.solar_panel_id WHERE PanelPerformance.output_power > 100 ORDER BY SolarPanels.installation_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT SUM(output_power) AS total_power FROM PanelPerformance GROUP BY performance_date HAVING performance_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT AVG(efficiency) AS avg_efficiency, MAX(efficiency) AS max_efficiency FROM SolarPanels GROUP BY installation_date HAVING MAX(efficiency) > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM solar_panels;
SELECT panel_id, manufacturer, efficiency FROM solar_panels WHERE installation_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT manufacturer, installation_date FROM solar_panels ORDER BY installation_date DESC;
SELECT panel_id, MAX(efficiency) AS max_efficiency FROM solar_panels GROUP BY panel_id;
SELECT * FROM panel_readings WHERE voltage >= 10 AND current >= 5;
SELECT * FROM solar_panels WHERE manufacturer = 'SunPower';
SELECT manufacturer, MAX(efficiency) AS max_efficiency FROM solar_panels GROUP BY manufacturer;
SELECT panel_id, installation_date FROM solar_panels ORDER BY installation_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT pr.panel_id, pr.reading_date, pr.power, sl.description FROM panel_readings pr JOIN maintenance_logs sl ON pr.panel_id = sl.panel_id;

SELECT p.manufacturer, pr.reading_date, pr.voltage * pr.current AS power FROM solar_panels p JOIN panel_readings pr ON p.panel_id = pr.panel_id WHERE pr.power > 50 ORDER BY pr.reading_date ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM solar_panels;
SELECT serial_number, efficiency FROM solar_panels ORDER BY efficiency DESC;
SELECT * FROM performance_data WHERE performance_score > 80;
SELECT panel_id, maintenance_date, maintenance_description FROM maintenance_logs WHERE panel_id = 1001;
SELECT panel_id, latitude, longitude FROM panel_locations WHERE latitude BETWEEN 30.0 AND 40.0;
SELECT id, serial_number, efficiency, installation_date FROM solar_panels;
SELECT * FROM performance_data WHERE performance_score > 0.8 ORDER BY data_timestamp DESC;
SELECT panel_id, AVG(performance_score) AS avg_score FROM performance_data GROUP BY panel_id HAVING avg_score > 0.7;
SELECT solar_panels.id, serial_number, latitude, longitude FROM solar_panels JOIN panel_locations ON solar_panels.id = panel_locations.panel_id;
SELECT maintenance_date, maintenance_description FROM maintenance_logs ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM solar_panels;
SELECT panel_brand, efficiency FROM solar_panels ORDER BY panel_brand DESC;
SELECT * FROM panel_performance WHERE energy_production > 1000;
SELECT panel_id, installation_date FROM solar_panels WHERE panel_type = 'Monocrystalline';
SELECT panel_id, latitude, longitude FROM panel_location WHERE address LIKE '%Street%';
SELECT * FROM solar_panels;
SELECT panel_id, panel_brand, installation_date FROM solar_panels ORDER BY installation_date DESC;
SELECT panel_id, panel_type, efficiency FROM solar_panels WHERE efficiency > 0.8 AND panel_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200 ORDER BY efficiency DESC;
SELECT p.panel_id, p.panel_brand, pe.energy_production FROM solar_panels p JOIN panel_performance pe ON p.panel_id = pe.panel_id WHERE pe.energy_production > 1000 ORDER BY pe.energy_production DESC;

SELECT p.panel_id, pi.issue_description, pl.address FROM solar_panels p JOIN panel_issues pi ON p.panel_id = pi.panel_id JOIN panel_location pl ON p.panel_id = pl.panel_id WHERE pi.status = 'resolved' ORDER BY pl.address ASC;
